Compare {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AdventureFriendlyWorld"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Adventure-Friendly World}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AnachronismStew"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Anachronism Stew}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CultureChopSuey"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Culture Chop Suey}}, and {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FantasyKitchenSink"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Fantasy Kitchen Sink}}. {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TechnologyLevels"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Technology Levels}} is what this trope averts. As well as {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MedievalEuropeanFantasy"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Medieval European Fantasy}}, of course. If the old stuff proves as effective as the new stuff, you\'92ve also got an {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ArchaicWeaponForAnAdvancedAge"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Archaic Weapon for an Advanced Age}}. It may also be the byproduct of a {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RetroUniverse"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Retro Universe}}. Contrast {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DaysOfFuturePast"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Days of Future Past}}. {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/JustForFun/IThoughtItMeant"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Not to be confused with}} tech used by schizophrenics.}